edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model

Interface AnnotationList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FormattableObject, java.lang.Iterable<Annotation>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RdfAnnotationList

    public interface AnnotationList
extends FormattableObject, java.lang.Iterable<Annotation>
    AnnotationList is a simple list of annotations without the additional metadata of pages.

    It is used as the incoming format in postAnnotation requests. The POST of a single annotation is implemented as posting a list of a single annotation, posting many is obviously a list.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Matthias Dressel, Michael Hitzker, Markus Hoefler, Andreas Loeffler, Timo Schmidt
